{"tid":2276424,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"鼻真係好重要","createTime":"2020-11-07T22:23:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-14T03:05:49.000Z","uid":180913,"like":9,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"96dd653558ed44d07b8fc6a525d6cbc933af107b","tid":2276424,"uid":180913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T22:23:51.000Z","msg":"鼻係最關鍵決定輪廓靚唔靚<br />\n其他五官唔好睇但係鼻好起碼都叫眉目清秀<br />\n鼻7其他五官正常俾會俾人感覺好蠢唔好睇<br />\n王祖藍個面形同埋隻眼其實唔差<br />\n但係鼻7就毀全相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n身邊朋友都話我個鼻真係好醜<br />\n老豆個邊9成親戚都鼻高直<br />\n啊媽個邊鼻短扁 成個柑咁<br />\n我就好彩鼻樑拎到老豆少少<br />\n但鼻翼鼻頭似啊媽個邊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係好似一個柑<br />\n<br />\n真係考慮左好多年<br />\n身邊人話都有鼻樑都有就唔好哂錢做<br />\n打下針縮下鼻咪算<br />\n但我真心接受唔到咁7<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n諗諗下又一年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n鼻梁骨就想保留<br />\n縮鼻縮翼如果唔隆鼻係唔係會好怪？<br />\n有無人做過？ 後遺症都多係唔係要定期保養"},{"pid":"c6516a27c63e8e638e1fce845f405cb95fc1bfaf","tid":2276424,"uid":180913,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T22:26:22.000Z","msg":"成個成龍鼻咁身邊人話我<br />\n好羨慕人細鼻個輪廓清秀"},{"pid":"a5965f96b519c2721674e982a60a53ea46600585","tid":2276424,"uid":135977,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T22:38:50.000Z","msg":"長戴口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e0293ebea5a5c1bec7239e8ccb512487ae3a004","tid":2276424,"uid":124439,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T23:27:20.000Z","msg":"個口 先至係囉"},{"pid":"35c821082e855cc32417c749a97c7ec26fc9d8db","tid":2276424,"uid":172297,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T23:32:30.000Z","msg":"樓主標準可以有幾低?王祖藍淨係鼻7咩?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢個孖潤腸呢？面型同頭型重7，好似舊壓扁左既面包咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13fbbb78e0010561c11aec5813b733d7c9645011","tid":2276424,"uid":97374,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T23:34:34.000Z","msg":"做你就做 唔好諗咁多咁多野講"},{"pid":"6da24d95257e84d58ae7430b2aa66d7c7dcff47d","tid":2276424,"uid":368910,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T23:37:25.000Z","msg":"係呀 啱青奴 雞柔個鼻就係好撚柒嘅表表者"},{"pid":"dfa9000a951694087e2ca4020bd531bc010f9a84","tid":2276424,"uid":8377,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"13fbbb78e0010561c11aec5813b733d7c9645011","tid":2276424,"uid":97374,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T23:34:34.000Z","msg":"做你就做 唔好諗咁多咁多野講"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T11:21:11.000Z","msg":"咪就係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n樓主諗咁多年 都仲得個諗字<br />\n佢都係算罷la"},{"pid":"1ff46e052da727aa903bbdac70af8d1bb09bc573","tid":2276424,"uid":8377,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T11:23:13.000Z","msg":"男人最緊要有錢 <br />\n鼻靚唔靚 who fucking care<br />\n<br />\n王祖藍 又矮 鼻唔靚又點？ 有錢有事業咪又一樣食到高妹"},{"pid":"41caf83916c78377831051058185f66661d0aad9","tid":2276424,"uid":8175,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T11:23:27.000Z","msg":"有冇圖 想像唔到成個柑咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edfdf86e14b50098c964c5299e6b82d96d79a3a8","tid":2276424,"uid":81702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"41caf83916c78377831051058185f66661d0aad9","tid":2276424,"uid":8175,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T11:23:27.000Z","msg":"有冇圖 想像唔到成個柑咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T11:39:58.000Z","msg":"係囉 淨係影個鼻嚟睇吓都好"},{"pid":"7a8ce3fefb7f474bb5b3809129520b6d290e4df1","tid":2276424,"ui